Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.54,0:00:03.67,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,對地進入角度、速度良好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.03,0:00:06.08,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,各機檢查對地進入系統
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.20,0:00:07.41,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,FLAT一號正常
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.58,0:00:08.61,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,FLAT二號正常
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.84,0:00:10.00,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,FLAT三號正常
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.10,0:00:11.58,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,FLAT四號正常
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.67,0:00:12.81,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,FLAT五號正常
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.97,0:00:14.15,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,FLAT六號正常
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.26,0:00:18.75,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,關上面部防護罩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.61,0:01:41.74,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,第一話  對月高呼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.39,0:01:46.63,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,這樣不熱嗎  羅蘭
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.97,0:01:47.99,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,可有意思了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.35,0:01:49.22,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,沒問題吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.72,0:01:52.00,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,啊  沒人會發現的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.71,0:01:54.78,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,多多保重  基斯  羅蘭
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.18,0:01:57.72,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,芙蘭·多爾你也保重了\N羅蘭你也別勉強啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.59,0:02:00.25,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,謝謝你  基斯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.04,0:02:43.06,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,沒射中  格威少爺
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.17,0:02:45.07,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,你是故意放走它的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.31,0:02:46.61,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,野狼逃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.96,0:02:48.40,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,那小伙子沒事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.48,0:02:54.24,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,不愧是我們的格威少爺
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.88,0:02:58.72,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,保重了  小伙子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.52,0:04:22.19,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,姐姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.78,0:04:24.20,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,那個孩子溺水了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.90,0:04:25.80,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,傑茜嘉！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.62,0:04:31.25,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,傑茜嘉！森姆你去下游！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.31,0:04:33.16,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,森姆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.41,0:04:33.93,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.58,0:04:52.45,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,他的臉色好轉了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.41,0:04:54.98,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,已經沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.58,0:05:03.65,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,別這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.47,0:05:10.90,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,一定是為了追這東西才溺水的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.45,0:05:14.19,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,外來人流落至此並不稀奇
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.95,0:05:16.62,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,傑茜嘉  拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.37,0:05:18.58,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,好的  小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.77,0:05:39.35,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.13,0:05:46.43,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,如果不是你溺水了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.28,0:05:51.41,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,我們海姆家才不准你這種外來人進入呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.04,0:05:53.19,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,蘇絲亞小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.54,0:05:55.77,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,你還是不要接近他為好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.14,0:06:13.49,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,無意接受恩惠\N我也有些錢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.90,0:06:15.81,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,我知道  羅蘭·塞亞克
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.16,0:06:19.41,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,我家收費很貴的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.16,0:06:21.63,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,那麼  我做工還給你們
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.24,0:06:24.30,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,你看過我的背囊了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.16,0:06:27.10,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,你不是也偷窺了我們洗澡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.42,0:06:29.48,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,溺水了看不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.16,0:06:30.84,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,真可惜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.03,0:06:32.89,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,是嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.78,0:06:36.07,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,比起我們姐妹倆\N你對這個更有興趣?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.47,0:06:38.19,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,請還給我！那是我的！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.47,0:06:39.00,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.30,0:06:40.04,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,怎麼這樣！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.15,0:06:42.66,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,你今晚有什麼打算?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.85,0:06:45.70,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,這個鎮裏有座海姆礦山
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.92,0:06:47.87,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,我準備去那裏做工落腳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.74,0:06:50.35,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,誒～ 原來你是有打算的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.21,0:06:52.22,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,海姆礦山…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.55,0:06:54.86,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,這裏是海姆先生的家?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.00,0:06:55.37,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.80,0:06:56.40,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,紀夏萊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.06,0:07:01.85,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,應該付多少錢?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.42,0:07:03.29,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.90,0:07:13.44,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.30,0:07:18.22,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,真的很像迪安娜陛下…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.58,0:07:22.80,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,本來為了參加成人式而清潔身體
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.06,0:07:24.55,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,卻被你破壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.98,0:07:25.72,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,我道歉！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.05,0:07:34.38,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,已經請求父親大人\N讓你在礦山做工
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.93,0:07:36.56,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,真的謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.73,0:07:40.72,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,我不知道那條河的水流那麼急
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.32,0:07:42.51,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,所以我才溺水了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.88,0:07:45.14,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,被你們救了  很感謝你們
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.02,0:07:46.65,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,我很快過去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.88,0:07:47.31,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.81,0:07:56.78,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,你也去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.00,0:07:58.53,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,是?  去哪裏?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.94,0:07:59.81,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,祭典啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.34,0:08:12.72,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,汽車過不了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.37,0:08:20.81,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,去西蓋爾山
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.92,0:08:24.11,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,去西蓋爾山！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.87,0:08:25.90,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,跟我來 出發啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.50,0:08:32.95,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,跟我來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.56,0:08:34.75,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,那個是你姐姐吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.18,0:08:35.60,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.40,0:08:43.40,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,後年輪到我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.48,0:08:45.68,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,小姐你們到此為止
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.25,0:08:48.00,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,你們今晚不可以再上去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.50,0:08:50.43,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,他們要進行通宵的祭典
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.97,0:08:52.25,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,我也是15歲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.38,0:08:53.39,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,外來人…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.88,0:08:54.86,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,喂！ 羅蘭！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.20,0:08:55.88,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,小姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.46,0:08:58.46,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,外來人不能再往上去的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.68,0:09:09.40,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,發現了會被趕下山的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.53,0:09:15.18,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,現在開始成人式的通宵祭典
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.80,0:09:18.00,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,各位成年人請離開這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.55,0:09:20.47,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,這就是WHITE DOLL嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.80,0:09:23.98,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,成年人下山  從前面快點下山！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.04,0:09:26.39,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,羅蘭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.88,0:09:32.53,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,下山吧  喝到天亮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.54,0:09:33.85,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,真羨慕年輕人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.58,0:09:37.07,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,羅蘭！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.67,0:09:38.49,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,你們真大膽！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.73,0:09:40.45,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,快下山
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.48,0:09:51.06,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,選擇自己的舞伴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.68,0:09:53.17,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,喂  姬艾爾  選我吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.06,0:09:53.17,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,姬艾爾  選我！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.18,0:09:57.22,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,姬艾爾今天真漂亮！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.10,0:10:17.89,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,爸爸的新型機  真厲害！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.95,0:10:26.36,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,比一比吧  看看有多快
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.64,0:10:31.86,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,好  你看著吧  新型機的性能
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.00,0:10:40.92,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,準備
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.79,0:10:44.73,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,很熱啊  快點弄完啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.40,0:10:46.22,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,羅蘭在哪裏?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.63,0:10:48.78,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,他在新豎井的升降台上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.23,0:10:53.94,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,羅蘭  活幹完了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.54,0:10:55.46,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,是…是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.70,0:10:57.20,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,海姆老爺要見你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.42,0:10:58.58,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,老爺要見我嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.10,0:11:02.90,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,老爺聽說你對機器很在行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.68,0:11:12.70,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,這就是格威少爺的最新式汽車啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.16,0:11:17.10,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,那個…  我是羅蘭·塞亞克
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.36,0:11:20.50,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,即使是轎車 也能像跑車一樣快哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.87,0:11:23.38,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,厲害！這裏也有座位!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.05,0:11:25.46,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,是格威少爺命人改裝的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.84,0:11:28.71,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,哇！全都閃閃發光
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.11,0:11:30.61,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,姐姐  很厲害啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.31,0:11:32.20,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,我看過了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.24,0:11:36.39,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,戰鬥機也需要嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.93,0:11:38.75,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,在海上的戰鬥也需要考慮
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.27,0:11:42.49,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,如果加利亞大陸進攻這裏的話\N的確有可能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.89,0:11:45.04,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,因此  必須繼續增加產量
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.55,0:11:46.43,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,這樣就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.87,0:11:49.74,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,進入其他領地的山區這樣的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.90,0:11:50.80,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,也請考慮
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.82,0:11:55.45,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,知道了  不過真的會開戰嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.89,0:11:56.72,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,傳聞而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.37,0:12:01.42,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,但是  我想利用這次機會\N建立工業化社會
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.09,0:12:03.18,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,不愧是少爺
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.70,0:12:07.02,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,繼承家業的同時\N也打算發展新時代的產業
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.73,0:12:10.90,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,既然在政治和外交都被老人家霸佔\N我也只能做這些吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.03,0:12:13.40,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,羅…叫羅蘭的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.96,0:12:14.99,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.98,0:12:18.14,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,羅蘭·塞亞克
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.42,0:12:21.56,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,你從今天起擔任我們的見習司機
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.28,0:12:23.50,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,私家車的司機嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.04,0:12:25.21,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,太好了  羅蘭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.11,0:12:27.97,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,父親大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.29,0:12:31.88,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,要抓緊空閒時間學習  考上大學
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.40,0:12:35.62,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,成為萊因福特少爺創造新時代的幫手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.60,0:12:37.94,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,那個…  你頭髮的顏色…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.27,0:12:38.83,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,是?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.53,0:12:40.35,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,我想起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.92,0:12:44.28,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,你頭髮的顏色\N跟被野狼襲擊的少年一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.55,0:12:48.85,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,非常感謝你！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.72,0:12:51.64,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,當時沒有殺掉它  我很擔心你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.90,0:12:54.82,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,托您的福\N我後來被這裏的兩位小姐救了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.10,0:13:00.01,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,既然大家有緣\N就更應該努力學習以報答少爺
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.80,0:13:01.42,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.67,0:13:02.85,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,太好了  羅蘭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.10,0:13:05.93,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,但是  新時代的學問很難的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.03,0:13:06.63,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,哈?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.83,0:13:08.74,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,是這樣吧?  格威少爺
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.50,0:13:12.80,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,是的  但是令尊很器重「羅拉」呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.09,0:13:16.90,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,今年我打算讓他參加遲了兩年的成人式
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.14,0:13:17.56,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.54,0:13:19.81,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,我能夠參加嗎!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.97,0:13:20.97,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,跟我一起嗎!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.43,0:13:23.96,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,我帶來的新式汽車在外面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.41,0:13:26.65,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,想試試你的技術 「羅拉·塞亞克」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.16,0:13:27.99,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,格威少爺…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.95,0:13:30.80,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,格威少爺  看天上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.90,0:13:32.16,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,那個是市民軍的飛行部隊吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.80,0:13:35.09,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,昆先生是個天才飛機師
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.63,0:13:40.00,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,部隊將全部由那種最快的飛機組編而成
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.69,0:13:41.72,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,踩油門
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.92,0:13:43.48,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.26,0:13:45.92,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,等待溫度計到中間…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.54,0:13:50.17,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.46,0:13:53.13,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,我想邀請姬艾爾小姐你參加\N這個夏天在城堡舉行的派對
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.46,0:13:54.81,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,在波斯托尼亞城堡嗎!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.16,0:13:55.88,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.43,0:13:58.27,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,兩位不反對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.58,0:13:59.43,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,怎麼會!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.67,0:14:03.56,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,小女能在波斯托尼亞城堡\N開始社交生涯  是我們的榮幸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.90,0:14:33.76,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,格威少爺一直將「羅蘭」稱為「羅拉」?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.95,0:14:40.63,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,差勁  所以才稱為「市民軍」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.12,0:14:43.71,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,有空的人到飛艇下集合
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.83,0:14:46.19,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,大佐  可以上來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.23,0:14:48.00,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,想去見少爺嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.40,0:14:50.50,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,因為他出資購買爸爸的飛機嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.13,0:14:55.16,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,胡說\N是我推薦了美雪爸爸的那部飛機
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.70,0:14:57.58,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,少爺只不過是出錢罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.60,0:15:00.82,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,爸爸！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.20,0:15:11.37,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,已經批量生產 不必擔心數量
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.07,0:15:13.00,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,這輛車就拿去用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.27,0:15:14.19,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,謝謝少爺
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.46,0:15:16.26,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,你的技術很好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.98,0:15:18.40,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,我很期待  羅拉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.56,0:15:20.08,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.44,0:15:21.79,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,bye
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.62,0:15:24.58,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,他叫「羅蘭」吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.84,0:15:25.82,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,是「羅蘭」沒錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.40,0:15:29.12,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,人手不夠吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.97,0:15:31.48,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,喂  別磨磨蹭蹭的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.90,0:15:33.13,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,開動馬達
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.68,0:15:34.96,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,取下那邊的錨鉤
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.38,0:16:22.54,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,我很快就出來 你在這裏等我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.85,0:16:23.25,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.16,0:16:25.92,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,我不去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.34,0:16:27.16,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,為什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.80,0:16:32.03,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,我才不會陪姐姐買\N派對時戴的首飾
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.03,0:16:34.93,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,這裏是迎合暴發戶品味的珠寶店
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.16,0:16:37.13,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,姬艾爾小姐的品味很好的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.07,0:16:39.56,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,羅蘭你總是稱讚姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.32,0:17:10.85,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,你看來混得不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.14,0:17:12.76,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,基斯你也不錯嘛  在麵包店工作嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.92,0:17:13.36,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.90,0:17:15.74,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,芙蘭也在諾克斯市工作
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.11,0:17:17.08,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,你跟芙蘭也見過面嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.11,0:17:18.50,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,去這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.60,0:17:21.70,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,我在域辛鎮的海姆家裏工作
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.79,0:17:24.61,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,在諾克斯市工作的朋友?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.55,0:17:28.25,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,家鄉的普通朋友而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.44,0:17:30.27,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,可以開車了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.16,0:17:35.75,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,昨晚的功課你做完了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.16,0:17:36.72,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.28,0:17:39.67,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,被凱特老師斥責只會浪費時間吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.20,0:17:49.68,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,對不起  因為我有事情\N所以要提早下課
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.96,0:17:51.65,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,不要緊  下周見
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.98,0:17:52.79,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,貴安
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.03,0:17:57.05,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,姬艾爾·海姆小姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.69,0:18:05.37,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,羅蘭 不在嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.74,0:18:37.37,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,總算來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.54,0:18:38.96,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,原來你一直在那裏嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.68,0:18:40.98,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,咦?  朋友?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.86,0:18:42.50,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,你還好吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.98,0:18:44.22,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,當然  基斯你也不錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.33,0:18:46.44,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,他們在談甚麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.73,0:18:49.86,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,搓麵粉的感覺很好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.16,0:18:50.54,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,好痛！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.96,0:18:55.09,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,很好吃啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.25,0:18:55.66,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.80,0:18:57.60,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,芙蘭·多爾呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.68,0:18:59.53,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,她說會來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.50,0:19:01.95,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,芙蘭！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.45,0:19:04.55,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,啊  不會是女孩吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.27,0:19:05.80,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,羅蘭！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.83,0:19:08.76,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,同鄉的聚會嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.77,0:19:10.84,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,我很想見你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.88,0:19:11.76,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,我也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.04,0:19:15.67,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,基斯的麵包很好吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.95,0:19:19.46,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,聽說芙蘭你在報社的印刷廠工作?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.88,0:19:22.82,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,是啊\N油墨的氣味根本洗不掉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.52,0:19:24.66,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,很香啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.48,0:19:26.99,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,那個女人想羅蘭吻她嗎!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.40,0:19:30.68,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,話說回來\N現在有信心在地球活下去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.00,0:19:32.48,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,住口！別說那種話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.08,0:19:37.24,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,不過啊\N我還以為在報社會第一時間得知消息
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.58,0:19:39.28,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,但完全沒有月球的新聞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.14,0:19:43.68,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,「加利亞大陸」進攻這裏的傳聞\N不就是指月球嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.36,0:19:46.17,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.80,0:19:49.57,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,羅蘭  那東西怎樣了?  沒問題吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.10,0:19:51.50,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,工作很忙  我沒去看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.76,0:19:55.56,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,FLAT已經自動鑽進山谷底部\N不會那麼簡單就被發現的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.82,0:19:57.78,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,在看什麼呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.80,0:19:59.76,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,他們三個…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.18,0:20:02.18,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,不過我有點擔心地震
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.96,0:20:04.31,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,你懂開車吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.66,0:20:07.05,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,沒錯  你離得近  去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.12,0:20:10.24,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,說得輕鬆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.88,0:20:22.37,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,紀夏萊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.51,0:20:26.76,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,聽說卡車要拿去修理啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.66,0:20:32.72,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,方向反了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.74,0:20:37.77,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,熄掉車頭燈比較好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.82,0:22:02.49,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.27,0:22:05.05,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,地球是個非常好的地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.46,0:22:08.84,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,快回來吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.49,0:22:12.46,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,地球是個非常好的地方！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.22,0:22:17.55,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,大家 快點回來吧！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.92,0:22:33.12,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,微熱尚未消退
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.59,0:22:39.83,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,少年低垂的眼簾
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.07,0:22:45.94,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,凝望心海
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.61,0:22:50.56,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,靜靜地微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.54,0:22:56.81,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,新生    消逝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.48,0:23:02.89,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,皆為宿命鐘擺的兩端
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.42,0:23:09.19,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,穿越挫折的黑暗所見的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.23,0:23:13.79,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,才是真正的光明
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.57,0:23:17.13,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,AURA
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.17,0:23:25.37,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,隨著黎明獻給被遺忘的星球
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.41,0:23:27.91,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,AURA
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.91,0:23:34.34,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,至高的愛就在這雙稚嫩的手中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.44,0:23:41.35,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,在域辛鎮成為我的故鄉當日
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.28,0:23:45.96,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,市民軍的人看見「迪安娜回歸軍」  反應過激
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.10,0:23:54.95,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,當石像「WHITE DOLL」崩塌時\N我也吃了一驚
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.00,0:23:57.62,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,因為機動戰士出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.24,0:24:01.00,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,次回 Turn A高達
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.70,0:24:02.43,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,成人式
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.60,0:24:04.55,main text,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,起風了

